data.description: Welcome to 125 Summerglen Ridge! This charming Newport News home features a semi-open floor plan that effortlessly flows from room to room. Bask in the abundance of natural light that floods the home, accentuating the beautiful new ceramic flooring throughout. Retreat to the upgraded bathrooms for a touch of luxury and relaxation. Conveniently located less than 2 miles from the upscale Marketplace at Tech Center, indulge in premier shopping and dining experiences. With its spacious layout, modern upgrades, and prime location, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Don't miss your chance to call it yours!
